title: Kenyan farm dam bursts, killing dozens
text:
Kenyan farm dam bursts, killing dozens 11:31am EDT - 01:28
A dam-burst on a rose farm in Kenya's Rift Valley has killed at least 47 people and swept away homes and power-lines. Two months of rain has already wreaked havoc in East Africa. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
